{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Web Workers 可以使用的函数和类","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>除了标准的&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 函数集 (例如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON\"><code>JSON</code></a> 等), DOM 有多种功能可供&nbsp;workers 使用。</p>\n\n<p>本文提供了一些列表。</p>\n\n<p><strong>Workers </strong>在另一个全局上下文内运行<strong>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> </strong>与当前<strong>&nbsp;window</strong>不同。</p>\n\n<p>默认情况下，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>的方法和属性不可用，但<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a>像 Window，实现<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a> 和 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"比较不同类型workers的属性和方法","title":"比较不同类型 workers 的属性和方法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"no-markdown\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td class=\"header\">Function</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Dedicated workers</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Shared workers</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Service workers</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Chrome workers <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Outside workers</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/atob\" title=\"atob()\"><code>atob()</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/btoa\" title=\"btoa()\"><code>btoa()</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/clearInterval\"><code>clearInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/clearTimeout\" title=\"clearTimeout()\"><code>clearTimeout()</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/dump\" title=\"dump()\"><code>dump()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>setInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\"><code>setTimeout()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\" title=\"importScripts()\"><code>importScripts()</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>no</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>yes, but is a no-op.</td>\n   <td>Unknown</td>\n   <td>no</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>yes, on <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>no</td>\n   <td>no</td>\n   <td>Unknown</td>\n   <td>no</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"apis_available_in_workers","title":"APIs available in workers","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"no-markdown\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td class=\"header\">Function</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Functionality</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Support in Gecko (Firefox)</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Support in IE</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Support in Blink (Chrome and Opera)</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Support in WebKit (Safari)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Broadcast_Channel_API\" title=\"Broadcast Channel API\"><code>Broadcast Channel API</code></a></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>允许在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin\">同源</a>的浏览<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Browsing_context\">上下文</a>（即窗口，制表符，框架或 iframe）之间进行简单通信（通常是来自同一站点的页面）。</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/38\" title=\"Released on 2015-05-19.\">38</a> (38)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Cache\" title=\"Cache\"><code>Cache</code></a></td>\n   <td>Cache API&nbsp;provides the ability to programmatically control cache storage associated with current origin.</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td>43</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Channel_Messaging_API\" title=\"Channel Messaging API\"><code>Channel Messaging API</code></a></td>\n   <td>Allows two separate scripts running in different browsing contexts attached to the same document (e.g., two IFrames, or the main document and an IFrame, two documents via a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a>, or two workers) to communicate directly via two ports.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/41\" title=\"Released on 2015-09-22.\">41</a> (41)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Console\" title=\"Console API\"><code>Console API</code></a></td>\n   <td>Provides access to the browser's debugging console (e.g., the <a href=\"https://firefox-source-docs.mozilla.org/devtools-user/web_console/index.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Console</a> in Firefox). The specifics of how it works vary from browser to browser, but there is a <em>de facto</em> set of features that are typically provided.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/38\" title=\"Released on 2015-05-19.\">38</a> (38)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></td>\n   <td>The <strong><code>CustomEvent</code></strong> interface represents events initialized by an application for any purpose.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/48\" title=\"Released on 2016-08-02.\">48</a> (48)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>Data Store</code></a></td>\n   <td>A powerful, flexible storage mechanism for multiple Firefox OS applications to use to store and share data between one another quickly, efficiently, and securely.</td>\n   <td>Only in Firefox OS internal (certified) applications, since v1.0.1.</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>DOMRequest</code></a> and <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>DOMCursor</code></a></td>\n   <td>Respectively, these objects represents an ongoing operation (with listeners for reacting to the operation completely successfully, or failing, for example), and an ongoing operation over a list of results.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/41\" title=\"Released on 2015-09-22.\">41</a> (41)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\" title=\"Fetch\"><code>Fetch</code></a></td>\n   <td>The Fetch spec provides an up-to-date definition of, and API for, fetching resources (e.g. across the network.)</td>\n   <td>Mostly in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/34\" title=\"Released on 2014-12-01.\">34</a> (34) behind pref, although a few features are later.</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td>42<br>\n    41 behind pref</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></td>\n   <td>This API allows asynchronous read of <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> objects.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/46\" title=\"Released on 2016-04-26.\">46</a> (46)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></td>\n   <td>This API allows synchronous read of <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> objects. This is an API that works only in workers.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/8\" title=\"Released on 2011-11-08.\">8</a> (8)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></td>\n   <td><code>FormData</code> objects provide a way to easily construct a set of key/value pairs representing form fields and their values, which can then be easily sent using the XMLHttpRequest <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest#send()\" title=\"XMLHttpRequest#send()\"><code>send()</code></a>&nbsp;method.</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span> (should be in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Released on 2015-06-30.\">39</a> (39))</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></td>\n   <td>The underlying pixel data of an area of a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\"><code>canvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> element. Manipulating such data can be a complex task better suited to be delegated to a Web Worker.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/25\" title=\"Released on 2013-10-29.\">25</a> (25)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API\" title=\"IndexedDB\"><code>IndexedDB</code></a></td>\n   <td>Database to store records holding simple values and hierarchical objects.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/37\" title=\"Released on 2015-04-07.\">37</a> (37),&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/42\" title=\"Released on 2015-11-03.\">42</a> (42) for <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IDBCursorWithValue\"><code>IDBCursorWithValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Network_Information_API\">Network Information API</a></td>\n   <td>provides information about the system's connection in terms of general connection type (e.g., 'wifi', 'cellular', etc.).</td>\n   <td>53.0 (53) only on mobile</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span> only on mobile</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API\" title=\"Notifications\"><code>Notifications</code></a></td>\n   <td>Allows web pages to control the display of system notifications to the end user</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/41\" title=\"Released on 2015-09-22.\">41</a> (41)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></td>\n   <td>The <strong><code>Performance</code></strong> interface represents timing-related performance information for the given page.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/34\" title=\"Released on 2014-12-01.\">34.0</a> (34.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>33.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></td>\n   <td>JavaScript objects that allow you to write asynchronous functions.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" title=\"Released on 2014-03-18.\">28</a> (28)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events\">Server-sent events</a></td>\n   <td>Allows a server to push data to a web page at any point, after a connection has been opened to it.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/53\" title=\"Released on 2017-04-18.\">53</a> (53) (currently only available in dedicated and shared workers; not service workers.)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration</code></a></td>\n   <td>You can register a service worker from inside a standard worker, and use associated functionality.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/40\" title=\"Released on 2015-08-11.\">40</a> (40)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></td>\n   <td>Create and return a new <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a>, or respectively <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a>, allowing to encode or decode strings into specific encodings.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/20\" title=\"Released on 2013-04-02.\">20</a> (20)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></td>\n   <td>Workers can use the static methods <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/window.URL.createObjectURL\">URL.createObjectURL</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/window.URL.revokeObjectURL\">URL.revokeObjectURL</a> with <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> objects accesible to the worker.<br>\n    Workers can also create a new URL using the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL/URL\" title=\"URL()\"><code>URL()</code></a> constructor and call any normal method on the returned object.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/21\" title=\"Released on 2013-05-14.\">21</a> (21) and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/26\" title=\"Released on 2013-12-10.\">26</a> (26) for URL() constructor</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a> with <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></td>\n   <td>WebGL (Web Graphics Library) is a JavaScript API for rendering interactive 3D and 2D graphics within any compatible web browser without the use of plug-ins.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/44\" title=\"Released on 2016-01-26.\">44</a> (44) behind a feature preference setting. In <code>about:config</code>, set <code>gfx.offscreencanvas.enabled</code> to true.</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></td>\n   <td>Creates and returns a new <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a>&nbsp; object; this mimics the behavior of the standard <code>WebSocket()</code> constructor.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/37\" title=\"Released on 2015-04-07.\">37</a> (37)</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></td>\n   <td>Creates a new <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>. Yes, workers can spawn more workers.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.5\" title=\"Released on 2009-06-30.\">3.5</a> (1.9.1)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span> See <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=31666\" rel=\"external noopener\">crbug.com/31666</a></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></td>\n   <td>The global scope of workers. This objects defines <a href=\"#workerscope\">worker-specific functions</a>.</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>The subset of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a> interface available to workers.</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.6\" title=\"Released on 2010-01-21.\">3.6</a> (1.9.2)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>The subset of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> interface available to workers.</td>\n   <td>Basic implementation <span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><br>\n    <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/appCodeName\"><code>appCodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/product\"><code>product</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/taintEnabled\"><code>taintEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/28\" title=\"Released on 2014-03-18.\">28</a> (28)<br>\n    <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/onLine\"><code>onLine</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/29\" title=\"Released on 2014-04-29.\">29</a> (29)<br>\n    <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>NavigatorLanguage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>: <span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/appName\"><code>appName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/appVersion\"><code>appVersion</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/onLine\"><code>onLine</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/platform\"><code>platform</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/userAgent\"><code>userAgent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>: 10.0<br>\n    Other: <span style=\"color:#f00;\">未实现</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></td>\n   <td>Creates and returns a new <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>&nbsp; object; this mimics the behavior of the standard <code>XMLHttpRequest()</code> constructor. Note that the <code>responseXML</code> and <code>channel</code> attributes on <code>XMLHttpRequest</code> always return <code>null</code>.</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Basic: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.5\" title=\"Released on 2009-06-30.\">3.5</a> (1.9.1)</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/response\" title=\"response\"><code>response</code></a> and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/responseType\" title=\"responseType\"><code>responseType</code></a> are available since <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/10\" title=\"Released on 2012-01-31.\">10</a> (10)</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/timeout\" title=\"timeout\"><code>timeout</code></a> and <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>ontimeout</code></a> are available since <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/13\" title=\"Released on 2012-06-05.\">13</a> (13)</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">Using web workers</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"比较不同类型 workers 的属性和方法","id":"比较不同类型workers的属性和方法"},{"text":"APIs available in workers","id":"apis_available_in_workers"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"除了标准的 JavaScript 函数集 (例如 String, Array, Object, JSON 等), DOM 有多种功能可供 workers 使用。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Functions and classes available to Web Workers","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Fonctions et classes disponibles dans les Web Workers","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Web Workers が使用できる関数とクラス","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Функции и классы доступные для Web Workers","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/web_workers_api/functions_and_classes_available_to_workers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/web_workers_api/functions_and_classes_available_to_workers/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API","title":"Web Workers API"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers","title":"Web Workers 可以使用的函数和类"}],"pageTitle":"Web Workers 可以使用的函数和类 - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}